e^{i\omega t}
H(\omega) = H(-\omega)
H(2 \pi) = H(- 2 \pi)
\cos(2 \pi t)
 h(t)*e^{i\omega t} = \int_{-\infty}^\infty h(\tau)e^{i\omega (t-\tau)}\,d\tau = \left[\int_{-\infty}^\infty h(\tau)e^{-i\omega \tau}\,d\tau\right]e^{i\omega t} := H(\omega)e^{i\omega t} 
 h(t)*\cos(\omega t) = h(t) * \frac 12 \left[e^{i \omega t} + e^{-i \omega t} \right] = \frac12 \left[H(\omega)e^{i \omega t} + H(-\omega)e^{-i \omega t}\right] 
